this January Friday the 13th I am PLAYING MY SECOND LIVE SHOW AS TALVI  W/ my favourite bands in the city ‼️

@homieshitmag x @vanscanada present a visceral experience with: 

9Million 
Webb
Talvi
MCDJ
Reeha

3D projections & set design by:
Marcus Jordan
Maddi Davis-Jones

This show will also be a coat drive. Free entry
with a donation of an old winter coat!💖

ATTENTION ‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️ i hardly ever play live shows and this one at (one of my favourite venues in the city) OWLS CLUB this Friday the 13th is going to be extremely special - i will be playing my solo music as ‘TALVI’ for the  first time ever w live backing with some of my favourite bands in the city @friendshiplounge and @matthewtomasi 
- plus it’s free entry with donation of a coat!

& 
a Halloween Party at the @acehoteltoronto that i’m hosting on the 29th (more info to come)
This SUNDAY OCT. 29th at the @acehoteltoronto at @evangelinetoronto i will be hosting a Halloween party and also PERFORMING at 9 pm sharp! come one come all. costumes required !!🎃🎃🎃🎃🎃🎃

HAPPY HALLOWE’EN
Thank you to everyone who came out to the @acehoteltoronto @evangelinetoronto for a very rare halloween TALVI performance. wish i could always sing in front of a lit fireplace - may have to put that in my rider. 
huge thanks to @quinnymills on guitar and @katduma who dj’d and did some backup vocals. 
photos by Donald Maclean Jr. ( more photos to come)❣️

to those of u who are fans of my music i have a single coming out this Friday January 12th called ‘A New Door is Closing’ so please mark your calendars! 
sorry for all the miscommunication about when my album comes out, and by miscommunication i mean me lying repeatedly about it. expect exciting things in the spring i have been working very hard!!!!
